snippet.title: Durango - Opening Movie
snippet.description:
모바일 개척형 오픈월드 MMORPG 야생의 땅: 듀랑고 오프닝 영상 공개!
브랜드 사이트를 통해 더 많은 영상과 스크린샷을 확인하세요.

Official Website - http://durango.nexon.com

Durango is an open-world MMORPG in which players are sent back in time to the prehistoric era. Open-world survival elements such as exploration, hunting, and community construction make Durango an experience neverbefore seen on mobile.

Check out the game site for more trailer and screen shots!
